<!-- ===== FEATURED COURSES (live from db) ===== -->
<section class="section section-alt" id="courses">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header-row">
      <div>
        <p class="section-label">Course Catalog</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">Featured programmes</h2>
      </div>
      <a href="/courses" class="btn btn-ghost">View all courses &#8594;</a>
    </div>
    <% if (featuredCourses.length) { %>
    <div class="catalog-carousel" data-catalog-carousel>
      <button type="button" class="catalog-nav catalog-nav-prev" data-carousel-prev aria-label="Previous">&#8249;</button>
      <div class="catalog-viewport">
        <div class="catalog-track" data-carousel-track>
          <% featuredCourses.forEach(function(course) { %>
          <div class="catalog-slide">
            <a href="/courses/<%= course.id %>" class="course-card-link">
              <article class="course-card">
                <div class="course-img course-img-<%= (course.id % 9) + 1 %> <%= course.image ? 'has-course-image' : '' %>"<% if (course.image) { %> style="--course-image: url('<%= course.image %>');"<% } %>>
                  <div class="course-category-tag"><%= course.category || 'General' %></div>
                </div>
                <div class="course-body">
                  <h3 class="course-title"><%= course.title %></h3>
                  <p class="course-description"><%= course.description %></p>
                  <div class="course-footer">
                    <span class="course-meta-pill">Professional Programme</span>
                    <span class="course-arrow">&#8594;</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </article>
            </a>
          </div>
          <% }); %>
        </div>
      </div>
      <button type="button" class="catalog-nav catalog-nav-next" data-carousel-next aria-label="Next">&#8250;</button>
    </div>
    <% } else { %>
    <div class="course-empty">
      <h3>No courses available yet</h3>
      <p>The course catalog is currently being prepared.</p>
      <a href="/courses" class="btn btn-primary">Open Courses Page</a>
    </div>
    <% } %>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== WHAT MAKES US DIFFERENT (FAQ) ===== -->
<section class="s-faq section" id="why">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="sfaq-head">
      <h2 class="sfaq-title">What Makes Us Different</h2>
      <p class="sfaq-sub">Osian Academy presents you the most personal learning experience recommended by our experts.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="sfaq-list">

      <div class="sfaq-item open" data-faq-item>
        <button class="sfaq-q" data-faq-question aria-expanded="true">
          Can beginners or non-IT students join Osian Academy?
          <span class="sfaq-icon">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="sfaq-a">
          <p>Absolutely. Our courses are designed for all levels — from complete beginners to working professionals looking to upskill. Every programme begins with fundamentals and your instructor adapts the pace to your starting point.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="sfaq-item" data-faq-item>
        <button class="sfaq-q" data-faq-question aria-expanded="false">
          Who will teach the courses at Osian Academy?
          <span class="sfaq-icon">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="sfaq-a">
          <p>All Osian instructors are working professionals with 5+ years of industry experience. They go through a rigorous selection and certification process. You learn from people who actively work in their field — not just teach it.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="sfaq-item" data-faq-item>
        <button class="sfaq-q" data-faq-question aria-expanded="false">
          Do you provide placement support?
          <span class="sfaq-icon">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="sfaq-a">
          <p>Yes. 100% placement assistance is included in every programme. This covers resume building, LinkedIn optimisation, mock interviews with industry professionals, and access to our hiring partner network of 100+ companies.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="sfaq-item" data-faq-item>
        <button class="sfaq-q" data-faq-question aria-expanded="false">
          Which courses are most in demand right now?
          <span class="sfaq-icon">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="sfaq-a">
          <p>Our most enrolled programmes are Web Development, Data Science & AI, Digital Marketing, Cybersecurity, and Cloud & DevOps. These fields have the highest job placement rates and fastest salary growth across the Indian IT industry.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="sfaq-item" data-faq-item>
        <button class="sfaq-q" data-faq-question aria-expanded="false">
          Can I join only as an online student?
          <span class="sfaq-icon">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="sfaq-a">
          <p>Osian Academy is 100% online — all sessions are conducted live on our platform. Students from anywhere in India (or abroad) can join. All you need is a laptop and internet connection.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="sfaq-item" data-faq-item>
        <button class="sfaq-q" data-faq-question aria-expanded="false">
          How soon can I get a job after completing the course?
          <span class="sfaq-icon">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="sfaq-a">
          <p>Most of our students receive interview calls within 30–60 days of completing their programme. Our career support team works actively with you throughout the placement process and maintains connections with 100+ hiring partners.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="sfaq-item" data-faq-item>
        <button class="sfaq-q" data-faq-question aria-expanded="false">
          Why should I choose Osian Academy for my career?
          <span class="sfaq-icon">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="sfaq-a">
          <p>Unlike batch-based platforms, every session at Osian is 1-on-1. Your instructor knows your progress, adapts to your pace, and is personally invested in your success. Combined with placement support, it is the most complete career-focused learning experience in India.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="sfaq-item" data-faq-item>
        <button class="sfaq-q" data-faq-question aria-expanded="false">
          What kind of placement support do students receive?
          <span class="sfaq-icon">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="sfaq-a">
          <p>Students receive: resume & portfolio review, LinkedIn profile building, mock interview sessions, referrals to our hiring network, and dedicated career counselling. Your instructor also provides ongoing mentorship during the job search.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="sfaq-item" data-faq-item>
        <button class="sfaq-q" data-faq-question aria-expanded="false">
          Are Osian Academy certifications recognised?
          <span class="sfaq-icon">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="sfaq-a">
          <p>Yes. Osian Academy certifications are verifiable online and recognised by our network of hiring partners. For select courses, we also prepare you for globally recognised certifications such as AWS, Google Cloud, Microsoft Azure, and CompTIA.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="sfaq-item" data-faq-item>
        <button class="sfaq-q" data-faq-question aria-expanded="false">
          Do you provide practicals and hands-on training?
          <span class="sfaq-icon">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="sfaq-a">
          <p>Every course includes live projects, assignments, and hands-on exercises conducted during sessions with your instructor. You graduate with a project portfolio that demonstrates real-world skills to employers.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="sfaq-item" data-faq-item>
        <button class="sfaq-q" data-faq-question aria-expanded="false">
          What makes Osian different from other training institutes?
          <span class="sfaq-icon">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="sfaq-a">
          <p>The 1-on-1 model. Every single session is private, live, and conducted by a dedicated expert instructor. No batch lectures, no generic recordings. Combined with personalised career support, Osian provides a level of individual attention that no other platform in India offers at scale.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

